Name: Elves Christmas Hentai Puzzle
About the game: On Elves Christmas Hentai Puzzle, you have to complete each girl’s picture by relocating, rotating, or swapping different tiles. Explore the small endearing castle full of paintings of beautiful elves, and enjoy the tranquility of the 3D map before taking on a new puzzle. The game offers a “random mode” that unlocks once you complete all puzzles. Features: Image matching puzzle gameplay Beautiful art 26 levels + 2 random modes Image gallery Streamer mode /
